column82: data exclusion stategy (value=1, ignore specific hours; value=2, ignore all data before the first midnight and after the last midnight)
column83: n hours ignored at start of meas (if data_masking_strategy=1)
column84: n hours ignored at end of meas (if data_masking_strategy=1)
column85: n days of measurement after which all data is ignored (if data_masking_strategy=1)
column86: epoch size to which acceleration was averaged (seconds)

column15: recalibration attempted with all available data, but possibly not good enough: Check calibration error variable to varify this
